name: Foolio
summary: Jacksonville rapper Julio Foolio was fatally shot in Tampa, Florida, on Saturday night. The shooting occurred at a hotel parking lot where Foolio was celebrating his 26th birthday. According to the rapper's attorney, it was an ambush. Foolio, whose real name was Julius Dubose, was pronounced dead at the scene. The investigation into the shooting is ongoing, and no arrests have been made at this time. Foolio's death is a significant loss to the Jacksonville hip-hop community, where he was known for his raw and authentic lyrics that often addressed the challenges of growing up in poverty and violence.
